        "When the shards on a table change all changefeeds connected to that table are disconnected. @mlucy believes that this is a leftover from when changefeeds always covered a whole table, and until #1774 is completed there is always a period when a shard moving involved a hole in coverage. But that assumption is no longer necessarily valid for point or range changefeeds since in some cases the changefeeds only cover specific shards, which might not become unavailable.\n"
